Package koopa.core.data

Interface Data

All Known Implementing Classes:
End, InWater, Marker, OnLand, ReplacementData, Start, Token, Tree
public interface Data
This is what Koopa really gives you: pieces of data, generated from an input source file. The data should help you make sense of the structure of that source.
